# LLM Configuration Example
# Copy this file to config.yaml and customize as needed

# Default provider settings
defaults:
  provider: azure
  model: gpt-4o
  max_retries: 3
  retry_delay: 1.0

# Provider-specific settings
providers:
  azure:
    # Azure OpenAI settings are loaded from environment variables:
    # - AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT
    # - AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY
    api_version: "2024-09-01-preview"

  gemini:
    # Gemini settings are loaded from environment variables:
    # - GEMINI_API_KEY
    # - GEMINI_PROXY (optional, defaults to http://127.0.0.1:7890)
    models:
      - gemini-2.5-flash
      - gemini-2.5-pro
      - gemini-2.0-flash

  claude:
    # Claude settings are loaded from environment variables:
    # - ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
    # - CLAUDE_PROXY (optional, defaults to http://127.0.0.1:7890)
    thinking_budget: 10000  # Token budget for thinking models
    models:
      - claude-sonnet-4-5
      - claude-sonnet-4-5-thinking
      - claude-opus-4-5
      - claude-opus-4-5-thinking


开启新会话	tmux new -s 会话名 (例如 tmux new -s claude)
离开会话（后台运行）	先按 Ctrl + b，松开后再按 d (Detach)
查看所有在跑的会话	tmux ls
重新进入某个会话	tmux attach -t 会话名
彻底关闭会话	在会话里输入 exit 或 tmux kill-session -t 会话名

左右分屏：Ctrl + b 然后再按 %
上下分屏：Ctrl + b 然后再按 " (引号)
切换面板：Ctrl + b 然后再按 方向键
关闭当前面板：输入 exit 或按 Ctrl + d
全屏/取消全屏当前面板：Ctrl + b 然后按 z (非常有用！)